this.handleChange = this.handleChange.bind(this); } handleChange(event) { const name = event.target.name; let keyval = event.target.value; let fdata = this.state.form2data fdata[name] = keyval this.setState({ form2data: fdata }) if (variants.f2variants[name]) { console.log(variants.f2variants[name][variants.f2variants[name].length - 1]) const minval = variants.f2variants[name][0][0] const maxval = variants.f2variants[name][variants.f2variants[name].length - 1][0] if (parseInt(keyval) < minval || parseInt(keyval) > maxval) { let newval = keyval.substring(0, keyval.length - 1) fdata[name] = newval this.setState({ form2data: fdata }) keyval = this.state.form2data[name] } for (let ind = 0; ind < variants.f2variants[name].length; ind++) { if (parseInt(variants.f2variants[name][ind][0]) === parseInt(keyval)) { document.getElementById(`sval_${name}`).innerHTML = variants.f2variants[name][ind][1] break; } else { document.getElementById(`sval_${name}`).innerHTML = '' } } } // console.log(ind) console.log(this.state.fvalue) console.log(event.target.value) } render() { return ( {/*
